{"about_the_game":"<br>The Arctic has always been a mysterious place. Running a motel in the Arctic is also a rare experience. Through the Arctic Motel Simulator, we not only want to simulate the climate and changeable weather of the Arctic, but also want to bring an Arctic-style motel management experience. This is reflected in the following aspects:<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/Section1_English.png?t=1739278826\" /><br>The Arctic is a vast and sparsely populated place. In the game, you will be able to expand the territory of the motel in the primeval forest.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/CutTree.gif?t=1739278826\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/Section2_English.png?t=1739278826\" /><br>It is not easy to find a motel in the Arctic. Motels there often provide many different types of services. In addition to providing various types of rooms for rent, shops selling Arctic specialties and restaurants offering Arctic cuisine can also earn you a lot of money. There are more, including laundries and other businesses waiting for you to discover.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/ExpandBusiness1.gif?t=1739278826\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/Section3_English.png?t=1739278826\" /><br>We have prepared eight room types for players to discover. Different room types have their own advantages, and players can choose freely according to their preferences.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/Igloo.gif?t=1739278826\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/Section4_English.png?t=1739278826\" /><br>Everyone knows that the winter in the Arctic is very cold, but the Arctic still has its own unique four seasons. We simulate the weather and temperature of the four seasons in the Arctic, as well as their corresponding gameplay, such as: controlling room humidity in summer and managing room temperature in winter, RVs that can be rented in spring, summer and autumn, and Arctic igloos in winter.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/Seasons.gif?t=1739278826\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/Section5_English.png?t=1739278826\" /><br>There are many wild animals in the Arctic, so legal hunting is allowed in many places. In the game, players can hunt legally in the winter hunting season. There are also several types of guns available in the game, and players can choose their favorite guns for hunting. Winter Arctic specialty recipes are also one of the purposes of hunting.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/PistolNoUI.gif?t=1739278826\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/Section6_English.png?t=1739278826\" /><br>Expanding a business can never rely on just one person. In the game, players can hire employees and special agents to expand the business of the motel. Players can train employees and arrange their work according to different focuses.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/Employee.gif?t=1739278826\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/Section7_English.png?t=1739278826\" /><br>The game is full of various random events, such as traveler partners investigating cheating, police patrolling your motel, health inspections, stranger events, etc. And due to insufficient police presence in the Arctic, the police also need your help in arresting wanted criminals.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/EventAndPeople.gif?t=1739278826\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Room 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3098470/185a8ceb535d0c2c832be68e4ff714717ecfb33a.jpg"},{"name":"Welcome!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3098470/13f7b81626974f5bca1f371047e652a79ef83290.jpg"},{"name":"Small Motel Business","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3098470/4d6ab55c57cf6b959aeb209522498a6faf9a9acd.jpg"},{"name":"Medium Motel Business","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3098470/6acb42c6dac1b4c05b33d9fb1242028cda2a83ff.jpg"},{"name":"Large Motel Business","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3098470/c91d3fa7a27933a6cffc0a2cf3248dbcd08b44fb.jpg"},{"name":"First Review!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3098470/5d3f43cad1fca2a9e20bae33d85ff3ef8a028d19.jpg"},{"name":"A Few Reviews","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3098470/cebd74c78756286e342d49cae212bab9768913ce.jpg"},{"name":"Some Reviews","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3098470/e61113377c096417a1c187f150ce699a9cbcc73c.jpg"},{"name":"Lots of Reviews","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3098470/e2f34ca6398651cf4381ef969c77afabad195b74.jpg"},{"name":"3 Star Motel","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3098470/7acb7a71520da202fb9c2930e51d97bdbecd7a5c.jpg"}],"total":100},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739278826","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/page.bg.jpg?t=1739278826","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/49aab2da53e6130881c4d6eeb174fd4cc9a0dbf7/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739278826","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/49aab2da53e6130881c4d6eeb174fd4cc9a0dbf7/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739278826","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h1>Join our Discord!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/JoinOurDiscord4.png?t=1739278826\" /></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><br>The Arctic has always been a mysterious place. Running a motel in the Arctic is also a rare experience. Through the Arctic Motel Simulator, we not only want to simulate the climate and changeable weather of the Arctic, but also want to bring an Arctic-style motel management experience. This is reflected in the following aspects:<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/Section1_English.png?t=1739278826\" /><br>The Arctic is a vast and sparsely populated place. In the game, you will be able to expand the territory of the motel in the primeval forest.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/CutTree.gif?t=1739278826\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/Section2_English.png?t=1739278826\" /><br>It is not easy to find a motel in the Arctic. Motels there often provide many different types of services. In addition to providing various types of rooms for rent, shops selling Arctic specialties and restaurants offering Arctic cuisine can also earn you a lot of money. There are more, including laundries and other businesses waiting for you to discover.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/ExpandBusiness1.gif?t=1739278826\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/Section3_English.png?t=1739278826\" /><br>We have prepared eight room types for players to discover. Different room types have their own advantages, and players can choose freely according to their preferences.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/Igloo.gif?t=1739278826\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/Section4_English.png?t=1739278826\" /><br>Everyone knows that the winter in the Arctic is very cold, but the Arctic still has its own unique four seasons. We simulate the weather and temperature of the four seasons in the Arctic, as well as their corresponding gameplay, such as: controlling room humidity in summer and managing room temperature in winter, RVs that can be rented in spring, summer and autumn, and Arctic igloos in winter.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/Seasons.gif?t=1739278826\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/Section5_English.png?t=1739278826\" /><br>There are many wild animals in the Arctic, so legal hunting is allowed in many places. In the game, players can hunt legally in the winter hunting season. There are also several types of guns available in the game, and players can choose their favorite guns for hunting. Winter Arctic specialty recipes are also one of the purposes of hunting.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/PistolNoUI.gif?t=1739278826\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/Section6_English.png?t=1739278826\" /><br>Expanding a business can never rely on just one person. In the game, players can hire employees and special agents to expand the business of the motel. Players can train employees and arrange their work according to different focuses.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/Employee.gif?t=1739278826\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/Section7_English.png?t=1739278826\" /><br>The game is full of various random events, such as traveler partners investigating cheating, police patrolling your motel, health inspections, stranger events, etc. And due to insufficient police presence in the Arctic, the police also need your help in arresting wanted criminals.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/EventAndPeople.gif?t=1739278826\" />","developers":["One Slice of Pizza Games"],"genres":[{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/header.jpg?t=1739278826","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257090600,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257090600/movie480.mp4?t=1737375890","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257090600/movie_max.mp4?t=1737375890"},"name":"Arctic Motel Simulator - Game